{"tid":1593552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"太古廣場現「我願榮光歸香港」直幡","createTime":"2019-09-25T06:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T06:48:38.000Z","uid":212626,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8f49f05b28042298153bffd51f1c4da2699e079e","tid":1593552,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T06:21:25.000Z","msg":"有反修例示威者發起到金鐘太古廣場懸掛直幡快閃行動，下午1時許，有人掛起一幅面積約2米乘16米、以黃底黑字寫上「我願榮光歸香港」的巨型直幡，直幡由商場二樓延至地面。現場有市民高喊反修例口號，包括「香港人加油」、「五大訴求、缺一不可」等，他們又高唱反修例歌曲以示支持，約20分鐘後，有商場保安上前向示威者了解，示威者拆除直幡後，人群散去。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4wrypPV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4wrypPV.jpg&h=7a0f4819&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/【修例風波】太古廣場現「我願榮光歸香港」直幡-190223\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E3%80%90%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2%E3%80%91%E5%A4%AA%E5%8F%A4%E5%BB%A3%E5%A0%B4%E7%8F%BE%E3%80%8C%E6%88%91%E9%A1%98%E6%A6%AE%E5%85%89%E6%AD%B8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E3%80%8D%E7%9B%B4%E5%B9%A1-190223&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9GZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=3a7025e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/【修例風波】太古廣場現「我願榮光歸香港」直幡-190223</a>"},{"pid":"0e4548975165e52cba61d42b7d4c14ab7b8301aa","tid":1593552,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T06:21:51.000Z","msg":"攬炒巴：香港人 928 929 全球見！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1593549\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1593549</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fe77e6f5248b51d319cd3fbd304decc23054b3a6","tid":1593552,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T06:25:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9558aeecee30c1a5fc3b5b2ab44c4aebadc2e591","tid":1593552,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T06:26:26.000Z","msg":"Wo<br />\n<br />\n入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/